Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.35,0:23:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}成長為人真是個可悲的故事啊
